 慣左就日日係到<br />\n日日見面 感情真係慢慢淡左<br />\n開始唔想佢係我到住 想要返啲自由 <br />\n想去邊就去邊 唔洗下下報到 <br />\n其實我覺得拍拖無問題 但唔好同居<br />\n唔係成日見面反而感情會仲好 會掛住對方<br />\n每日返到屋企就係到講公事<br />\n朋友生日想玩夜啲都有說話<br />\n唉 好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cafe82872e13a8097e44381180faa4fa350a87f8","tid":260454,"uid":99621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:59:51.000Z","msg":"隔離post有10年散咗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實最後都會歸於平淡，<br />\n我都想同你過一世，<br />\n也都只想同你過一世。"},{"pid":"a896374c584efea28dc67775507554ee5201301f","tid":260454,"uid":124812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T06:20:16.000Z","msg":"同女朋友一齊左7年<br />\n從高中到而家做野，<br />\n人地睇好似好好，但係自己知自己事<br />\n一齊係開心但一諗未來就會嘈<br />\n我想做興趣<br />\n但係佢想穩定<br />\n慢慢就大家都唔想面對呢個問題。<br />\n<br />\n都係會冇左之前個種感覺<br />\n好懷念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aabbc509026efbfbcf7f60f5dc2dfb5af9b65b3b","tid":260454,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T06:57:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1abc855b0c7be9be6d44a864a511cdf18ebc8af7","tid":260454,"uid":102300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T06:58:41.000Z","msg":"冇以前噤愛 習慣左係身邊 唔識珍惜 自私 <br />\n唔係結婚對像嘅咪byebye lo"},{"pid":"a9abc8425e0b1b19cd1d9f6817e041d95930317d","tid":260454,"uid":102300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T07:01:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>愛情需要保鮮，兩方都要主動去維繫感情，唔係點樣過一世<br />\n如果嘗試歌你仲係冇曬感覺，證明緣盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"